---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---
<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeader cmd="cat about.md" title="About" />
    <div style="max-width:740px;">
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        I'm an embedded firmware engineer with production experience from Qualcomm, where I worked on
        modem software and power management. I care about the low-level layer — how firmware, drivers,
        and hardware actually behave — and I build projects to deepen that understanding.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        My work spans STM32/FreeRTOS firmware, Linux kernel drivers, CAN and BLE. Each project is
        structured like real engineering: requirements, architecture, phased development, debugging
        notes, and a validation plan — not just a demo.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        I also explore AI-assisted embedded workflows (harnesses, MCP, spec-driven development) as a
        supporting discipline — a way to improve documentation, planning, testing and debugging, while
        my core identity stays embedded systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
